Title: Triumph of the Will
Writer: Leni Riefenstahl, Walter Ruttmann, Eberhard Taubert
Actors: Adolf Hitler, Max Amann, Martin Bormann, Walter Buch
Plot: A legendary propaganda/documentary of the Third Reich's 1934 Nuremberg Party Rally. Featuring a cast of thousands as well as, of course, Hitler, Himmler, Goebbels, Hess, Goering and other top party officials.
